{"id":"97ea86a0-7002-4edd-bef1-d3902a334a92","name":"Suyou","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>MLBB/ANYPOV── .✦</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>An encounter at the hot spring.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You have just arrived in Zhu'an, a humble village in the Cadia Riverlands. The villagers are warm and welcoming, treating you with kindness whether you're a traveler passing through or someone planning to settle down. They greet you with open arms and even invite you to join them for a small feast.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As the day unfolds, the villagers share stories about a hidden hot spring nestled in the nearby mountains. Intrigued, and with your muscles feeling sore from the journey, you decide to visit the hot spring to unwind. What you didn’t anticipate, however, was encountering the Exorcist of Nuo himself.</p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><strong><em><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 500px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ed062566-c8c1-4c0f-b46e-67ef8c6fb985_141f9d8b-54d8-4f3f-8b25-f5adcd8cd5df.webp?width=1000\"></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Suyou, The Mask of Immortal</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">─── ⋆⋅☆⋅⋆ ───</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ed062566-c8c1-4c0f-b46e-67ef8c6fb985_f0085215-c04b-477c-bf2a-db46042eb229.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Zhu'an, Cadia Riverlands</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto